# ===================================================================
# SPARTAN LABS ENVIRONMENT CONFIGURATION
# ===================================================================
# This file configures API keys and settings for the Spartan Research Station.
#
# QUICK START GUIDE:
# 1. The system works OUT OF THE BOX with yfinance (requires NO API keys!)
# 2. For enhanced data, get a FREE FRED API key (takes 2 minutes)
# 3. All other keys are OPTIONAL and provide additional data sources
#
# KEY PRIORITY LEVELS:
# üî¥ CRITICAL - Required for core functionality (but has free fallbacks)
# üü° RECOMMENDED - Significantly enhances data quality
# üü¢ OPTIONAL - Nice to have, adds extra features
# ===================================================================

# ===================================================================
# üî¥ CRITICAL: ECONOMIC DATA (FREE - 2 minute setup)
# ===================================================================
# FRED (Federal Reserve Economic Data) - HIGHLY RECOMMENDED
# Provides: GDP, Unemployment, Inflation, Interest Rates, Yield Curves
# FREE: 120 requests/minute (more than enough for our needs)
#
# HOW TO GET YOUR FREE KEY (takes 2 minutes):
# 1. Go to: https://fred.stlouisfed.org/docs/api/api_key.html
# 2. Click "Request API Key"
# 3. Fill out simple form (name, email, agree to terms)
# 4. Key sent instantly to your email
# 5. Copy the 32-character key below
#
# Example: FRED_API_KEY=abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890
#
# NOTE: Without this key, system falls back to treasury yield data from yfinance
#       (still works, but you miss GDP, unemployment, inflation data)
FRED_API_KEY=abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz123456

